&lt;p&gt;Today I rented a car to drive to class. I got the Pontiac Sunfire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;#8217;s white with a little spoiler on the back. One cool feature is the back seat folds down expanding the trunk into the cabin of the car.&lt;/p&gt;
